Class Bucket

  • java.lang.Object
    • Bucket

  • public class Bucket
extends java.lang.Object
    Uses multiple instances of Rectangle to model a Bucket. This class represents a Bucket object. When combined with the GameArena class, instances of the Bucket class can be displayed on the screen.
